<item>
            <title>[LU-17062] Prevent use after free following *_decref_locked() usage</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17062</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In rare cases when one of:&lt;br/&gt;
lnet_peer_net_decref_locked&lt;br/&gt;
lnet_peer_decref_locked&lt;br/&gt;
lnet_peer_ni_decref_locked&lt;br/&gt;
Actually destroys the object it is not safe to use.&lt;br/&gt;
Update the functions to return true when the object is deleted and ensure the object is not referenced (used) after it has been kfree()&apos;d.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
